## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8852-102">一个`SpeechDetected`引发事件<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-102">A `SpeechDetected` event is raised by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> classes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8852-103">**SpeechDetected**识别引擎可以识别为人类语音的音频输入时，将生成事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-103">**SpeechDetected** events are generated when a recognition engine can identify audio input as human speech.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8852-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechDetectedEventArgs> 派生自 <xref:System.EventArgs>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechDetectedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8852-105">下面的示例创建一个处理程序<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-105">The example below creates a handler for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8852-106">该处理程序初始化显示每次检测到语音，并显示状态信息，包括音频位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-106">The handler initializes a display every time speech is detected and displays status information, including audio position.</span></span>  
  
```  
_recognizer.SpeechDetected +=  
  delegate(object sender, SpeechDetectedEventArgs eventArgs)   
  {  
  
    // Clear previous recognition information.  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Enabled = true;  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Visible = true;  
    Utils.DisplayAudioInputFormat(_audioStateLabel, _recognizer);  
    Utils.DisplayRecognizerState(_recognizerStateLabel, _recognizer.State);  
    Utils.DisplaySpeechDetected(_speechDetectedLabel, eventArgs.AudioPosition);  
  };  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8852-109">下面的示例创建一个处理程序<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-109">The example below creates a handler for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8852-110">该处理程序初始化的显示每个时间语音检测到并显示状态信息，包括音频位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8852-110">The handler initializes a display each time speech is detected and displays status information, including audio position.</span></span>  
  
```  
_recognizer.SpeechDetected +=  
  delegate(object sender, SpeechDetectedEventArgs eventArgs)   
  {  
  
    // Clear previous recognition information.  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Enabled = true;  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Visible = true;  
    Utils.DisplayAudioInputFormat(_audioStateLabel, _recognizer);  
    Utils.DisplayRecognizerState(_recognizerStateLabel, _recognizer.State);  
    Utils.DisplaySpeechDetected(_speechDetectedLabel, eventArgs.AudioPosition);  
  };  
```
